{
  "stem": "26486.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When I left the north of France?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Paris was just Paris.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, there was nothing special in Paris.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There's always-- Paris is always special.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] But I mean, I was living with my parents and there was nothing special.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I always wanted to get some work, which I did.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Pardon me.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Almost right away I found work, dancing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And dancing at the-- I danced at the Moulin Rouge in Paris, too, which was very exciting.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know, with the [LAUGHS] ooh-la-la.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[LAUGHTER] Now, that was nice.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I liked it there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then I danced at the opera.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I, I take-- I took the place with Solange Schwarz who was one of the big opera dancers.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we played in And my sister was first dancer, and I was the second dancer.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very little.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Very poor.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I couldn't tell.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But very poor. 700 French francs a month. 750, I think it was.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was very poor.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was looking for work.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He didn't have any work.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was during the beginning of the war-- very hard.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was an interpreter when he-- you know, when he found different things to do as an interpreter, he would do it.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He would do anything when he found it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Excuse me I have to-- may I?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Excuse me.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When I-- after '38, you mean?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Off and on when they needed me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, I was like fill-in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I worked there for about-- I worked like that for about, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] '38, '39-- not very long.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because then I met Simone.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I worked with her at the Chamber of Commerce.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then I left the dancing for a while.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The war was coming on.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
